          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For checking of the system's linearity, 20 lines of",
                "Co-56 with energies from 733.77 keV to 3548.11 keV and",
                "26 gamma-lines of Ga-66 from 833.6keV to 4805.3keV were",
                "used.The relative efficiency of the detector was",
                "determined by means of standard sources Zn-65, Co-56,",
                "Na-22, Mn-56,Co-60 and Ga-66.",
                "Absolute normalization of gamma line intensities was",
                "made by Cr-53 8884 keV gamma-line yield, using data",
                " from G.A.Bartholomew et al. Canad.J.Phys,44,2111,1964,",
                "A.N.Rudak et al. J.YE,1,235,1965 and A.V.Rudak et al.",
                "J,YF,5,504,1967"
